verse_part: falling on his knees before Him
when they had dug an opening
(that is to say, given to God)
full of what was left over
it is for those for whom
A VAT UNDER THE WINE PRESS
and they wounded him in the head
to those who are nursing babies
and began to give false testimony
he had been accustomed to do
You who are going to destroy
as they were reclining at the table
